on U.S. access to a site at Kumchang-ri in the Democratic People's
Republic of Korea, his spokesman said on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
"The agreement confirms his strong belief that a determined
diplomatic effort can resolve even the most serious issues,"
spokesman Fred Eckhard said.
</P>
<P>
