Kanombe Airport that the crucial element in the conflict in the
DRC is Sudan and the Interahamwe who are in the DRC at the
invitation of that country's authorities.
</P>
<P>
On the flaring war in the Horn of Africa, they appealed to the
leaders of Ethiopia and Eritrea to stop the war and seek a
peaceful solution to the conflict. They decided to send a joint
delegation to these two countries to convey their feelings and
concern.
</P>
<P>
They also reviewed progress made in various areas of bilateral
cooperation and examined ways of further strengthening that
cooperation. 
