<HEADLINE> Work on Macao's Handover Smooth: Chinese Vice Premier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Qian, who arrived here earlier today to attend the inaugural
ceremony of Macao Cultural Center scheduled for Friday, said Sino-
Portuguese relations are "good" in general.
</P>
<P>
Qian made the remarks when he met with representatives from the
Sino-Portuguese Joint Liaison Group, Xinhua News Agency Macao
Branch and other Chinese institutions stationed in Macao.
</P>
<P>
