<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 18 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
March 19, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at 17:
00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -1 degree C., max. 7 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
