<TEXT>
<P>
NUWARA ELIYA (Sri Lanka), March 18 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan
President Chandrika Kumaratunga Thursday called for a stronger
presentation of the South Asian Association of Regional
Cooperation (SAARC) on the international arena with an aim to
promote regional prosperity.
</P>
