<P>
DAR ES SALAAM -- All the Burundi warring factions have agreed
that security should be guaranteed to the repatriation of Burundi
refugees and internally displaced people to their homes.
</P>
<P>
Sources in Tanzanian northern town of Arusha said Wednesday
that delegates from the just concluded 10-day committee meeting on
